Funciones auxiliares:
sameType(tipoA, tipoB) {
tipoA == tipoB
}
paramsEquals(paramsDefinition, p) {
int index = paramsDefinition.indexOf(p)
return index >= 0 AND index < paramsDefinition.size AND sameType(p.type, definition.get(index).type)
}
existReturn(ifSentences, elseSentences) {
return ifSentences.contains(return) AND elseSentences.contains(return)
}
Conjuntos auxiliaries:
SimpleTypes = {intType, realType, charType}
ReturnableTypes = {intType, realType, charType, voidType}
** Se guarda en una variable el valor anterior.
